Static variable:
------------------
-> common data for all objects.


req:
capture stu name + stu roll + stu colleage.


in a class,
declare stu name + stu roll as instance varibales.
declare stu colleage  as static variable.

-> static variable or class variable
-> memory is allocated only one time
-> memory is allocated during class loading
-> static variable can be accessed without creating obj
static varible can be accessed using class name.